# Message Query Tests
# Test message retrieval and search endpoints

@baseUrl = http://localhost

### Get Messages by Session ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/session/test_session_123456789
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Messages by Session ID with Limit
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/session/test_session_123456789?limit=10
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get Messages by Contact (remoteJid)
GET {{baseUrl}}/messages/contact/256703722777@s.whatsapp.net
